4	0	2	PF NO.:7
4	3	2	PF NO.:8
0	3	2	PF NO.:9
0	3	2	
0	3	2	
1	3	2	PF NO.:10
1	3	2	
1	0	2	PF NO.:11
1	0	2	
1	0	7	PF NO.:12
1	0	7	
1	0	7	

The number of page faults using LRU are 12
